It will be fine and cool to warm over all of South Africa on Sunday, the South African Weather Service says. GAUTENG: Fine and cool. MPUMALANGA: Fine and cool, but warm in the Lowveld. LIMPOPO: Fine and cool to warm. NORTH WEST: Fine and warm. FREE STATE: Fine and cool. NORTHERN CAPE: Morning fog along the coast and adjacent interior, otherwise fine and cool, but warm in the north. The wind along the coast will be moderate south-easterly. WESTERN CAPE: Morning fog in the west and south-west at first, becoming partly cloudy, otherwise fine and cool but warm over the eastern interior. It will become partly cloudy along the south coast by afternoon. The wind along the coast will be moderate south-easterly along the west coast, otherwise moderate west to south-westerly. WESTERN HALF OF THE EASTERN CAPE: Fine and cool, but warm over the interior.  It will become partly cloudy in the extreme south-west in the evening. The wind along the coast will be light north-westerly, becoming fresh south-westerly in the afternoon. EASTERN HALF OF THE EASTERN CAPE: Fine and cool. The wind along the coast will be light north-easterly, becoming moderate south-westerly in the afternoon. KWAZULU-NATAL: Morning fog over the interior, otherwise fine and cool but warm in the east. The wind along the coast will be moderate to fresh north-easterly. The temperature in your area: Pretoria: 6°C - 23°C Johannesburg: 5°C - 21°C Nelspruit: 9°C - 24°C Polokwane: 3°C - 24°C Potchefstroom: 3°C - 24°C Mafikeng: 6°C - 25°C Rustenburg: 3°C - 24°C Bloemfontein: 2°C - 23°C Welkom: 4°C - 22°C Bethlehem: 0°C - 21°C Upington: 10°C - 28°C Kimberley: 5°C - 27°C Cape Tow: 12°C - 16°C George: 8°C - 20°C Beaufort West: 12°C - 27°C Port Elizabeth: 11°C - 22°C East London: 13°C - 25°C Durban: 12°C - 25°C Pietermaritzburg: 6°C - 26°C  Click here to see the specific forecast for your city over the next few days  GET THE NEWS at your fingertips and download the News24 app for Android here now. Get it for your iPhone her